PrecisSetting apart, for the use and benefit of the GOD'S LAKE FIRST NATION, of some 481 hectares of land including mines and minerals situated in unorganized territory of northern Manitoba approximately 185 kilometres from the urban centre of Thompson, as an addition to Esker Ridge A Indian Reserve, in Manitoba.
